name: ArcanaMix
description:
◆ArcanaMix

  • This model is adjusted to output mainly kawaii illustrations.

◆Donate

https://www.buymeacoffee.com/hemlokai

  • If you would like, please make a donation to help us continue our activities.

◆Model Overview

V1

  • Sampler: DDIM or DPM++ SDE Karras recommended.

  • Steps: 40~

  • Clipskip: 2

  • CFG Scale: 5~8

  • Denoise strength: 0.4-0.6

  • Quality tags (masterpiece, best quality, etc.) are not required. You can add your own.

  • We recommend embeddings separately.

◆Sample

Disclaimer

  • The creation of SFW and NSFW images is at the discretion of the individual creator.

  • This model is not a model created to publish NSFW content in public places, etc.

License

If you do, please be aware you have to include the same use restrictions as the ones in the license and share a copy of the CreativeML OpenRAIL-M to all your users (please read the license entirely and carefully)
